{"tid":789220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"莫拉達：我想入多過30球","createTime":"2018-08-22T05:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T15:17:36.000Z","uid":31314,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"58830c42043571663ad7e1fecb15f6b4aa49aaf8","tid":789220,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"這位西班牙前鋒以7000萬鎊身價從皇家馬德里加盟「藍戰士」，首季攻入15球，但在干地麾下主張直接踢法時，他發揮不出水準。<br />\n<br />\n現在在新帥沙利帶領下，沒有如傳聞般離隊的莫拉達希望重拾水準：「上季對我來說不容易，缺乏信心，加上傷患，但一旦穿上射門鞋，一切就不同了。當然我希望可以入多於30球，但我寧願攻入15或20球，然後球隊贏到英超或其他大賽。球隊是最重要的。」"},{"pid":"85b71a673a88db437b2e08e18ab6f6cd17cbe351","tid":789220,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"今年有無人賭<br />\n雖然舊年條垃圾走數"},{"pid":"6d0c8f549b9e9bbd637f189ea333dd7408be4b74","tid":789220,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"最撚好就緊係一球唔洗用又拎到盃啦屌<br />\n莫拉達識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c6250e8cde74547414539be8a11ae33da1cd69","tid":789220,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"今年阿古獸拎多"},{"pid":"033afcff96325d5d36493b295f057b6f4ff8a3eb","tid":789220,"uid":5264,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"唔睇返都醒唔起條友值成70m<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b69c5badb71cea2eb43489ca26fb90a37dbe6e","tid":789220,"uid":14029,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"你今季入到10球 我代我老死引戰王飲水塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bb1fe192e83fd58fcdf84cb545da98f8f0da7e","tid":789220,"uid":76147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"某會員飲晒城門水塘啲水未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ce16e0cff5300496276a03dd62fdaaaf01a2ae","tid":789220,"uid":8775,"like":0,"